docs.lead_paragraph: Inbee Park is trying to win her fourth major this year, but the potential historic moment has a wrinkle: women’s golf now has five majors, so it’s unclear what constitutes a Grand Slam.
docs.abstract: No one has accomplished a women's golf Grand Slam, but as Inbee Park tries to win her fourth major this year at the Women's British Open, the addition of a fifth major this year has created confusion about golf's definition of a Grand Slam.

headline.main: Grand Slam ... Maybe: Park Seeks Win at British Open
